latest version of this software is available at the following URL:
http://www.pablotron.org/software/raggle/.

Introduction
============
Raggle is a command-line RSS aggregator, written in Ruby
(http://www.ruby-lang.org/).  

System Requirements
===================
* REXML, version 2.4.0 (or newer):
  http://www.germane-software.com/software/rexml/
* NCurses-Ruby, version 0.7.1 (or newer):
  http://ncurses-ruby.berlios.de/
* YAML-Ruby, version 0.49.1 (or newer):
  http://www.yaml.org/

